headline: WEC Energy Group announces offering of Convertible Senior Notes due 2028
summary: WEC Energy Group, Inc. (NYSE: WEC) today announced that it intends to offer, subject to market and other conditions, $700,000,000 in aggregate principal amount of its convertible senior notes due 2028 (the "convertible notes") in a private offering to qualified institutional buyers pursuant to Rule 144A under the Securities Act of 1933, as amended (the "Securities Act").
